Happiness is a day at the pool in @melashotels
••
Starting my day with a Turkish coffee by the pool.
After some days in istanbul I decided to visit the beautiful city of Antalya, couldn’t ask for a better place than @melashotels to discover the real Turkish hospitality experience.
